    "updated_at": "2014-10-15T13:20:27Z",
    "body": "Hello,\n\nDo you still have this bug if you launch Atom with this command:\n\n```\nenv UBUNTU_MENUPROXY=0 atom\n```\n\nIf not, #708 should fix this bug :-)\n\nNote that it's strange to set this environment variable to `1` but ok.\nWe could check if `$UBUNTU_MENUPROXY == libappmenu.so` but they can change the name or we can use another (custom) menu proxy.\n"
  },
